{"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"What if the penalties in football were more like the penalties in the corporate world? What if, instead of negating any forward progress, penalties were simply subtracted from the gains?"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This would create a remarkably different game. There’d be penalties on every down! A holding call on a 15 yard run would result in a 10 yard gain. Penalties would no longer be a deterrent to illegal play, they’d just be part of a good strategy."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/brunow\/06-07-corporate-and-football-penalties"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Brunow"}],"color":{"standardColorIdentifier":"purple"},"platforms":[{"introducedAt":"2017.01.20","name":"Brunow"}],"title":"Corporate and Football Penalties"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2015"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/06-07-corporate-and-football-penalties","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"topicSectionsStyle":"detailedGrid","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"date: 2015-06-07T21:55:14-05:00"}],"references":{"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/Archive":{"title":"Archive","type":"topic","role":"collectionGroup","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/brunow\/archive","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"All posts"}]},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/2015":{"title":"2015","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2015","url":"\/documentation\/brunow\/2015","kind":"article","role":"collectionGroup","abstract":[],"type":"topic"},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow":{"role":"collection","url":"\/docum